  "description": "Giveaway Plugin",
  "readme_markdown": "<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-giveaway-plugin\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#giveaway-plugin\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Giveaway Plugin</h1>\n<p>Create a giveaway on your server</p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-command-list\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#command-list\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Command List</h2>\n<pre><code>/glist\n</code></pre>\n<p>This command is for showing all giveaways to the player\nPermission: giveawayplugin.list</p>\n<pre><code>/gcreate\n</code></pre>\n<p>This command is for creating a giveaway\nPermission: giveawayplugin.create</p>\n<pre><code>/gend\n</code></pre>\n<p>This command is for ending a giveaway\nPermission: giveawayplugin.end</p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-permissions\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#permissions\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Permissions</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Permission</th>\n<th>Default</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>giveawayplugin.list</td>\n<td>player</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>giveawayplugin.create</td>\n<td>op</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>giveawayplugin.end</td>\n<td>op</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<script defer src=\"https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js/v8c78df7c7c0f484497ecbca7046644da1771523124516\" integrity=\"sha512-8DS7rgIrAmghBFwoOTujcf6D9rXvH8xm8JQ1Ja01h9QX8EzXldiszufYa4IFfKdLUKTTrnSFXLDkUEOTrZQ8Qg==\" data-cf-beacon='{\"version\":\"2024.11.0\",\"token\":\"508eb1d242ef46b690a0886422106e77\",\"r\":1,\"server_timing\":{\"name\":{\"cfCacheStatus\":true,\"cfEdge\":true,\"cfExtPri\":true,\"cfL4\":true,\"cfOrigin\":true,\"cfSpeedBrain\":true},\"location_startswith\":null}}' crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>",
